wdi2-SE.XPD.TERT.ZS.def: Expenditure on tertiary education is expressed as a percentage of total general government expenditure on education. General government usually refers to local, regional and central governments.
wdi2-SE.XPD.TERT.ZS.name: Expenditure on tertiary education
wdi2-SE.XPD.TERT.ZS.source: UNESCO Institute for Statistics (http://uis.unesco.org/). Data as of February 2020.
